      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "CUP is basically just about wedge bonding messing with FEOL structures I think due to strain-induced bandgap effecs, and bonding mechanics being a little different if you have certain structures under the pad which would necessitate tuning the bonding process parameter to account for that difference.",
