      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Why'd you have issues with minimum litho dimensional openings in the SiN that have minimum top metal expansion underneath?\nEssentially bond pads so tiny no relevant wire bond house will want them, but large though for the litho to not cause problems?",
